    	<div class="comment_content">
    		<p>Hi lovedos, thanks for your interest in the list and your comment.  Here is the breakdown firms by country: China (136 companies), Japan (258 companies) U.S. (524 companies).  When you look at these figures, you may say that China still has a long way to go to catch them both, bit over the years these countries are moving in opposite directions in terms of list presence..  Since we started publishing the list in 2004, U.S. and Japan have been on the decline, while China&#8217;s presence is growing each year. I hope this helps clarify.</p>

    	</div>

		
